# Assets Module

## PURPOSE
Static assets for the extension (icons, images, fonts).

## CONTAINS
- /icons: Extension icons in multiple sizes
  - icon16.png (16x16)
  - icon32.png (32x32)
  - icon48.png (48x48)
  - icon128.png (128x128)
- /images: UI images and graphics
- /fonts: Custom fonts (if needed)

## ICON REQUIREMENTS
- Must provide multiple sizes for different contexts
- Use transparent backgrounds
- Follow browser extension icon guidelines
- Optimize file sizes

## REFERENCES
- Parent: /.windsurf (root context)
- Used by: manifest.json, /src/ui/*

## RULES
- Optimize all images for web
- Use SVG where possible for scalability
- Keep total asset size minimal
- Follow brand guidelines
